stas revolucionarios y la pandemia del Covid-19"><span class="td-page-meta" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"><meta itemprop="url" content="https://www.socialistalternative.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/stock-exchange-4880802_1280.jpg"><meta itemprop="width" content="1280"><meta itemprop="height" content="913"></span>    </footer>

